# Dev (recommended): Vite proxies /api → http://localhost:3000
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api

# Or call the API directly (backend CORS must allow your frontend origin):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000/api

# Production (Vercel): Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-backend.example.com/api

# Public marketing site (optional — defaults shown in src/config/publicSite.ts)
# VITE_SUPPORT_EMAIL=support@your-school.com
# VITE_SUPPORT_URL=https://help.example.com
# VITE_TERMS_URL=https://example.com/terms
# VITE_PRIVACY_URL=https://example.com/privacy
# VITE_DEMO_VIDEO_URL=/videos/demo.mp4
